=========
1. Track which dice are saved and carry over to next roll

  - When "roll" btn displays and is clicked, check which els have class "selected" and add a class "saved"

=========

2. Re-roll dice which weren't saved from previous roll

  - When firing new roll, don't re-roll the els with class "saved"

=========

3. Prevent "saved" els from being unselected/unsaved on later rolls

  - if el has "saved" class, don't remove class "selected" + any store data stuff

=========

4. Once 5 dice are selected/saved, tally total score and save

=========

5. Save scores per player and compare to determine rankings

=========

6. Have previous round's loser start the next game

